<br />
<p style="font-size: 1.0em;font-weight: bold;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">1.  General Guidelines</p>
<br />
<p style="font-size: 0.8em;font-weight: bold;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">A.  By using or visiting the Veam website, providing content to Veam, or using any Veam products, software, data feeds, and/or services (collectively, the "Services"), in addition to the Terms of Service, you agree to the following general guidelines:</p>
